         explicitly false to match the docs/05-privacy.md §七 promise
         that update checks are user-initiated only. The feed URL is
         populated once the CI pipeline in PR β starts publishing
         appcast.xml alongside the release .zip. SUPublicEDKey is a
         placeholder in PR α and gets swapped for the real key when
         PR β lands. -->
    <key>SUFeedURL</key>
    <string>https://github.com/jchunf/Pulse/releases/latest/download/appcast.xml</string>
    <key>SUPublicEDKey</key>
    <string>__SPARKLE_PUBLIC_ED_KEY__</string>
